    About BDI Baltic Exchange Dry Index

    The contributing timecharter averages to the BDI are as follows: 40% Capesize {BCI14TC Index DES<GO>}, 30% Panamax {BPRATCR Index DES<GO>}, 30% Supramax {BSI58TC Index DES<GO>}. The index was first published on January 4 1985 at 1000 points. Last trading day: Christmas Eve. Index units measured in: Points
